  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you and your Puppets become more adept at molding chakra.</p><p> When you or Puppets cast a jutsu, you can always exclude each other from any negative effects the jutsu may cause.</p><p> You and your Puppets can exclude up to 2 other creatures from such effects, spending 5 chakra per creature.</p><p> Also, all Puppets you possess gain the Jutsu Specialization Upgrade once for free.</p><p> Your Puppet Tool gains an additional jutsu each time it gains this Upgrade.</p><p></p>",
